@base = http://localhost:7331

### Ping — observe X-Correlation-ID and X-Response-Time in response headers
GET {{base}}/api/ping

### Ping with custom correlation ID (forwarded back in response)
GET {{base}}/api/ping
X-Correlation-ID: my-trace-123

### Internal endpoint — no key (→ 401)
GET {{base}}/api/internal

### Internal endpoint — with key (→ 200)
GET {{base}}/api/internal
X-Internal-Key: dev-internal-key

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### OpenAPI docs (browser)
GET {{base}}/docs
